name: Telepisodes
description: Watch TV shows, movies and sports events
overview:
Telepisodes is a video search website that contains links to different videos of TV shows, movies and sports events. Results and data provided by the site are a mix of submission from different registered users and simple search algorithm that automatically populate information on the site from different genre of films, television shows and various sports events today.

Telepisodes also performs as an episode guide of television series and video content specifying the air schedule, channels where it airs and let users contribute their favorite shows and links online.

The official Facebook page of the site can be found at https://www.facebook.com/Telepisodes and twitter account @Telepisodes.
